name: FACE EXTERNE // recto&verso
description:
“You are ignorant, you don't understand anything, because you haven't woken up. Your judgments are a mistake, you are children of stagnant epochs, you sacrifice your world for death”.
You believe them, believe, because they tried to cover up their horror with a good purpose. They are heroes, they are saviours, they are a ray of light that will illuminate the path of millions of lost souls. Their sermons are bright and fiery, their clothes sparkle from blue screens like diamonds in the sun. Their temple is woven by their invisible nets, it is their place of power. But they are all just infantile fools, rotting from the inside. Getting under their skin, you discover fear and pain, numbness before life.Isn't it funny that you didn't notice how they tied you up?
